text.tspan: Confirmed deaths, including all victims and attackers who died as a result of the incident.
Note: The Global Terrorism Database is the most comprehensive dataset on terrorist attacks available and recent data is complete. However, we
expect, based on our analysis, that longer-term data is incomplete (with the exception of the US and Europe). We therefore do not recommend
this dataset for the inference of long-term trends in the prevalence of terrorism globally.
